 "05.png", "id": "1833449600394486", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974579_1833449603727819_6400319588012020426_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QP_DBRuNavYQ7kNvgF5FZHM&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBwP0oOvqbk8hzTQ1P7mRhtFx_vsQ95vVK8y60yC77IMQ&oe=677A7105"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cricket X Banner .png", "id": "578704851567805", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75505860_578704854901138_2146439193637587985_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QUsdetbFwB0Q7kNvgHL4Kqb&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCvrTMtC3SYZTJw9X8zAKdCuM__auLQGGBHsKu6NdawPg&oe=677A72C8"}, "display_name": "Cricket X", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Cricket X \u2013 The Ultimate VR Cricket Experience on Meta Quest!\nStep into the crease with Cricket X, the most immersive and realistic VR cricket game designed to sharpen your batting skills and deliver hours of entertainment. Whether you\u2019re chasing thrilling targets, perfecting your shots, or taking on exciting challenges, Cricket X is the ultimate VR cricket training simulator for players of all levels.\n\nGame Modes\n\u2022\tChallenge Mode: Set your target score, overs, and wickets. Chase totals and test your strategy and accuracy.\n\u2022\tTraining Mode: Recreate any delivery you want by customizing swing, spin, speed, bowler type, bounce, and pitch pace. Set the line and length to perfect every shot and refine your skills.\n\u2022\tDemo Mode: Face deliveries with increasing difficulty, with voice-over hints announcing each ball\u2014keeping you focused and ready.\n\u2022\tSpecial Challenge Mode: Take on thrilling challenges featuring unique and unpredictable deliveries to push your batting skills.\n\nKey Features\n\u2022\tDay & Night Mode: Play in dynamic lighting for a realistic stadium feel.\n\u2022\tRealistic Physics: Experience true-to-life ball swing, spin, and bounce.\n\u2022\tReplay & Analytics: Analyze your shots with replays, pitch maps, and scoring zones.\n\u2022\tBatting Styles: Switch between left-hand and right-hand batting seamlessly.\n\u2022\tReal Bat Support: Attach your controller to a real bat for maximum immersion.\n\u2022\tPassthrough Mode: Play safely with real-world visuals around you.\n\nPlay Cricket X \u2013 The Next Level of VR Cricket!", "short_description": "A Virtual Reality Cricket Simulator game with realistic physics where you can chase thrilling targets."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://xrevstudiopk.blogspot.com/2023/08/xrev-studio.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Xrev Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://cricketx.net/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "9087187121361147"}, "review_messages": ["", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/86625133_1125590695756555_7161271893592578981_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mr4zaLCFBXgQ7kNvgHHdaJK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB820ciTmBbZX-oG0bHfa3uyAgBScbfMWIalbAoEZ4gFg&oe=677A78FA"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Cricket X", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "contex