odes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "990736352029405"}]}, "change_log": "New Challenges in Challenge Mode:\nYorker Precision Test: Prove your mastery by handling toe-crushing yorkers with pinpoint accuracy.\nBouncer Accuracy Blitz: Dominate bouncers with perfect timing and unmatched skill.\nCutter Clean Connection: Tackle deceptive off cutters and leg cutters to showcase your elite batting finesse.\n\nAdded Special Deliveries Mode: Special deliveries mode where you can play exciting deliveries with voice over of what's coming next.\n\nTutorial Mode Unleashed: A fully interactive mode designed to teach new players every essential aspect of Cricket X, setting you up for success from the first ball.\n\nNext Ball Button Reimagined: Redesigned to perfectly complement the game\u2019s immersive theme, making every interaction seamless and stylish.\n\nMain Menu Lobby Design Changes: Updated with minor design enhancements for a cleaner and more polished look.\n\nCricket Ball Redefined: Introducing a completely revamped cricket ball design for a strikingly realistic bowling experience.\n\nScoreboard Revolution: The scoreboard gets a full overhaul, delivering crystal-clear updates to keep you effortlessly in sync with every match.\n\nBowling System Enhanced: Rebuilt from the ground up for an unparalleled experience, with expert difficulty fine-tuned to challenge even the pros.\n\nUI Perfectly Positioned: Game settings and analytics are now thoughtfully aligned with the batting side, offering unparalleled convenience for players.\n\nBug Fixes & Optimization: Numerous issues squashed and refinements made to deliver a smoother, sharper, and more thrilling experience.\n", "created_date": 1735306914, "id": "9132373200175872", "version": "1.9.8b", "version_code": 74, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}